---
title: Creamy Chicken Rigatoni with Zucchini and Tarragon
description: This cozy pasta dish is simple but tasty, thanks to a few key flavour additions - leeks, lemon zest and tarragon! This dinner is simplicity at its best.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-rigatoni-b707fa4a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/creamy-chicken-rigatoni-f15709dd.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/creamy-chicken-rigatoni-581b5ebcbfba3d6530441792
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Italian
course: main course
servings: 2
